div.h1: Jump to User Mode: Stack Setup for iret
div.p: Kernel stack layout before executing iret to enter ring 3
Critical: CS.RPL (bits 0-1) = 3 tells CPU to enter Ring 3. This triggers privilege level change CPU pops SS and ESP.

ol.li: If CPL changes: Pop ESP, Pop SS

div.p: asm jump_to_user_mode: mov eax, [esp + 4] ; entry point mov ebx, [esp + 8] ; stack top

pre.code:
; Load user data segments mov ax, 0x23 ; User data (index 4, RPL=3) mov ds, ax mov es, ax mov fs, ax mov gs, ax
; Setup iret stack frame push 0x23 ; SS (user data segment) push ebx ; ESP (user stack top) push 0x202 ; EFLAGS (IF=1) push 0x1B ; CS (user code segment) push eax ; EIP (entry point)
iret ; Jump to ring 3!
